Class ActionWrapperDataFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.core.rules.actions.ActionWrapperDataFactory

  • public class ActionWrapperDataFactory
extends Object
    The factory for creating ActionWrapperData.

    This helps to hide and enforce the relationship between ActionAnalysisDataKey, ActionAnalysisData, Action, and Artifact.BuildArtifact

        public <T extends AbstractAction> com.google.common.collect.ImmutableMap<ActionWrapperDataFactory.DeclaredArtifact,Artifact.BuildArtifact> createActionAnalysisData(Class<T> actionClazz,
                                                                                                                                                                    BuildTarget target,
                                                                                                                                                                    com.google.common.collect.ImmutableSet<Artifact> inputs,
                                                                                                                                                                    com.google.common.collect.ImmutableSet<ActionWrapperDataFactory.DeclaredArtifact> outputs,
                                                                                                                                                                    Object... args)
                                                                                                                                                             throws ActionCreationException
        Creates the ActionWrapperData and its related Action from a set of ActionWrapperDataFactory.DeclaredArtifacts. The created ActionWrapperData is registered to the ActionAnalysisDataRegistry.

        This will materialize the declared ActionWrapperDataFactory.DeclaredArtifacts into Artifact.BuildArtifacts that can be passed via Providers to be consumed.

        Type Parameters:
        T - the concrete type of the Action
        Parameters:
        actionClazz -
        target - the built target
        inputs - the inputs to the Action
        outputs - the declared outputs of the Action
        args - the arguments for construction the Action
        Returns:
        a map of the given ActionWrapperDataFactory.DeclaredArtifact to the corresponding Artifact.BuildArtifact to propagate to other rules
        Throws:
        ActionCreationException
